		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Ok thanks. I was a bit confused.. Some games (Golf comes to mind) sets Y-scroll to $FF all the time. I wonder why it didn't set $00 and set the nametable it should be displaying instead, since it never scrolls anyway..(?)

		

		</td>
