	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well we didn't program the game so we can't know. One reason might be so that vertical sprite offset that are rounds numbers are aligned to tiles the background. Writing $ef would be more "correct", but it will only affect the first scanline which is often considered overscan.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


